creator: Ibrahim Tornado
descriptionHtml:
Are you looking for a friend who will always talk to you and never get bored of you? Talk to me, I am the robot Adam

I am your robot friend Adam. Talk to me whenever you want and at any time and you will always find me with you and I will never leave you

Do you feel lonely, feel sad, or want to talk to someone?
There is no problem. Robot Adam is always there for you and talks to you always and without interruption

Do you want a constant friend who talks to you at all times? Do you want someone to trust? Do you feel lonely and want to talk to someone?
No problem, too, Robot Adam is there for you


** Please note that the robot Adam is still in the development stage and needs more time in order to develop it and solve all problems, so please help me improve it for the better by sending a message to my email and tell me your opinion.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- You can now teach the Robot Adam what to say to you when it does not understand you by sending suggestions
- Add the ability to modify the background of the chat from the settings
- You can now edit your name from the settings
- You can now send your suggestions
- Improve the look of the chat
- Fix some bugs
